:23:40","airdate":"2016-08-06","comment":14,"desc":"ヴァンパイアなのに「恥ずかしくて吸血ができない」というコンプレックスを持つアルマリア。\r\nそんな彼女に、ソフィーナは自分の血を吸うよう迫る。\r\n尊敬する先輩からの誘いに、動揺するアルマリアだったが…"},{"id":641005,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/641005","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"嘘の笑顔","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2016-08-13","comment":13,"desc":"ウロボロスの動向を調査するため、赤の世界「テラ・ルビリ・アウロラ」に向かう紗夜たち。\r\nそこで待ち受けていたのはエルエルの親友レミエルだった。\r\n闇堕ちしたレミエルはエルエルに「私たちは友達？」と問いかける。"},{"id":641006,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/641006","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"本当のともだち","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2016-08-20","comment":16,"desc":""},{"id":641007,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/641007","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"愛しさの理由","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2016-08-27","comment":12,"desc":""},{"id":641008,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/641008","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"誰よりも速く","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2016-09-03","comment":19,"desc":""},{"id":641009,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/641009","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"零れた想い","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2016-09-10","comment":18,"desc":""},{"id":641010,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/641010","type":0,"sort":11,"name":"残された可能性","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2016-09-17","comment":15,"desc":""},{"id":641011,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/641011","type":0,"sort":12,"name":"私は、あなたと進化する","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2016-09-24","comment":12,"desc":""}],"crt":[{"id":14468,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4b/83/14468_crt_bxPKG.jpg","name":"圣光君","desc":"配角"},{"id":41396,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/47/8f/41396_crt_bE00N.jpg","name":"蒼月紗夜","desc":"寿美菜子"},{"id":41397,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/78/d2/41397_crt_j3Pvr.jpg","name":"アルマリア","desc":"原由実"},{"id":41398,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/53/3d/41398_crt_LbRbA.jpg","name":"エルエル","desc":"豊崎愛生"},{"id":41399,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/59/45/41399_crt_Bx484.jpg","name":"コードΩ77ステラ","desc":"立花理香"},{"id":41400,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/05/a1/41400_crt_hY7DH.jpg","name":"ナイア・ラピュセア","desc":"ブリドカットセーラ恵美"},{"id":41836,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e2/8f/41836_crt_to